            "Fusion of classic structures with regional ingredients"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Trend influence:"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "items": [
            "Experimental menus",
            "Cultural storytelling through drinks"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
